1
00:01:25,220 --> 00:01:27,186
=The Land of Warriors=

2
00:01:27,188 --> 00:01:29,980
(Adapted from Tangjia Sanshao's novel
"Soul Land")

3
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:34,300
=Episode 33=

4
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,780
If you lose, you lose.

5
00:01:38,812 --> 00:01:40,280
It doesn't matter.

6
00:01:40,710 --> 00:01:41,730
No matter?

7
00:01:42,270 --> 00:01:44,220
You said it so casually.

8
00:01:44,316 --> 00:01:46,399
But the one who went undercover
for twenty years

9
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,420
is me.

10
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,980
Your undercover wasn't for nothing.

11
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,730
Tiandou has suffered a heavy blow.

12
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:56,140
I only didn't expect

13
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,283
you would lose to Tang San.

14
00:01:58,284 --> 00:02:00,056
I didn't lose to Tang San.

15
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:01,730
I lost to you.

16
00:02:02,172 --> 00:02:04,795
If you were not eager to get rid
of the Tiandou soul master army

17
00:02:04,796 --> 00:02:06,747
and forced me to seize power
as soon as possible,

18
00:02:06,748 --> 00:02:09,224
I would have handled all this
more carefully.

19
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,899
I would never

20
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:13,190
let Tang San have the opportunity
to save Xue Ye.

21
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:16,229
All grown up,
but still acts like a child.

22
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:17,829
Do you really think you're still

23
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:19,719
that child crying out for her mother?

24
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,740
Mother?

25
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:25,300
I, Qian Renxue, have no mother.

26
00:02:26,076 --> 00:02:27,848
Don't tell me you've forgotten,

27
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,780
Your Holiness.

28
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:31,340
Mother!

29
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,759
Mother, don't send me away.

30
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,109
I will be a good girl.

31
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:38,690
I promise I will cultivate diligently.

32
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:53,999
Mother,

33
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,669
it hurts.

34
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:56,039
Help me.

35
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,250
Bear with it.

36
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,220
If it weren't for your bloodline,

37
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,370
you don't even deserve this soul bone.

38
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:18,370
Can I stay if I overcome this pain?

39
00:03:45,670 --> 00:03:46,690
My face...

40
00:03:47,276 --> 00:03:49,549
This soul bone is one
of the Angel's Armor pieces

41
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:52,650
passed down in Martial Soul Hall
for generations.

42
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,690
It can disguise your martial soul,

43
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,780
appearance, and voice.

44
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:01,810
The real Xue Qinghe is gone.

45
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,250
From now on,

46
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,690
you are Xue Qinghe.

47
00:04:05,790 --> 00:04:06,439
Mother.

48
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,650
Don't call me that.

49
00:04:11,628 --> 00:04:13,069
I will remember that,

50
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:13,780
Mother...

51
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,060
I mean,

52
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,610
I will remember that,

53
00:04:18,550 --> 00:04:19,580
Your Holiness.

54
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,380
You made me realize

55
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,900
that I never had a mother.

56
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:34,490
In this world,

57
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:35,900
I only have one family.

58
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,880
That person is Grandfather.

59
00:04:38,350 --> 00:04:39,580
Your Holiness,

60
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,140
I'll ask Grandfather

61
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,170
for permission to manage the Elder Hall.

62
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,739
From now on,

63
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:48,060
we'll divide our powers
and go our separate ways.

64
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,220
At the moment

65
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,090
I realized you saw me as a pawn,

66
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,780
I woke up.

67
00:05:15,004 --> 00:05:17,592
Did you think
I spent twenty years going undercover

68
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,490
just to fulfill your plan?

69
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:22,900
No,

70
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:25,410
I'm only loyal to myself.

71
00:05:27,990 --> 00:05:29,260
I will make Tiandou

72
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:31,780
my power.

73
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:35,490
The moment I take the throne

74
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:38,900
will be the moment I declare war on you.

75
00:05:39,276 --> 00:05:40,600
I may have failed

76
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:42,140
in taking over Tiandou.

77
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,260
But I still have the Elder Hall.

78
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,380
Don't forget

79
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:47,820
that Elder Hall

80
00:05:48,204 --> 00:05:50,700
is the true power center
of the Martial Soul Hall.

81
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,220
Those Flamens

82
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:55,460
are the highest decision-makers.

83
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,530
I won't follow your orders anymore.

84
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:01,380
Just stay in your place.

85
00:06:04,348 --> 00:06:06,504
You're overestimating yourself.

86
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:08,530
With your current strength,

87
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,410
you want to control the Elder Hall?

88
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,850
Even your grandfather

89
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,260
wouldn't agree.

90
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,730
This confrontation

91
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,595
has revealed Xue Qinghe's true face

92
00:07:49,596 --> 00:07:51,279
and the Martial Soul Hall's conspiracy.

93
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,900
But Tiandou and the Martial Soul Hall
are now at war.

94
00:07:54,790 --> 00:07:55,850
Future struggles

95
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:58,170
will only be more cruel.

96
00:07:58,840 --> 00:07:59,530
San,

97
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,749
tell us

98
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,580
about your fight with Qian Renxue.

99
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,460
Strong.

100
00:08:04,604 --> 00:08:05,700
She's very strong.

101
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,650
We managed to rescue His Majesty

102
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:09,340
mostly because of luck.

103
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,730
Qian Renxue's

104
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:13,279
Angel Martial Soul
is incredibly powerful.

105
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,429
I used all my strength

106
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,187
to break through her Angel Domain.

107
00:08:16,188 --> 00:08:18,309
If Wu hadn't merged
her consciousness and body

108
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:19,959
at the critical moment

109
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:20,970
and fought her,

110
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:23,340
we would have lost.

111
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:28,410
Six-winged Angel Martial Soul
and Angel Domain?

112
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,309
I remembered Qian Xunji's martial soul

113
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,848
was also a Six-winged Angel.

114
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,340
Qian Renxue must have inherited
his martial soul.

115
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:36,460
I once guided her cultivation.

116
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:38,610
I clearly remember her martial soul

117
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,429
is the Swan Martial Soul
of the Tiandou royal family,

118
00:08:41,430 --> 00:08:43,130
with only five soul rings.

119
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,060
What's going on?

120
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,130
Does

121
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,490
she have Twin Martial Souls?

122
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:56,580
It's disguise.

123
00:08:58,430 --> 00:09:00,187
It should be

124
00:09:00,188 --> 00:09:01,992
the legendary Angel's Armor.

125
00:09:03,430 --> 00:09:04,700
I've never heard of it.

126
00:09:04,940 --> 00:09:07,435
There's finally something
that you don't know.

127
00:09:07,436 --> 00:09:10,669
The Martial Soul Hall has kept
these six soul bones for a millennium.

128
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,420
They're known as the Angel's Armor.

129
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:15,189
Only a soul master
with a Six-winged Angel Martial Soul

130
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:16,250
can use them.

131
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:17,940
And all of them

132
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:19,759
are now on your master?

133
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,300
Yes,

134
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:22,340
that's why he's so powerful.

135
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:23,770
Do you know

136
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:26,039
the soul bone skills
of the Angel's Armor

137
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,610
can provide dual disguises,

138
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,643
changing both appearance and voice

139
00:09:29,644 --> 00:09:31,736
and even disguising the martial soul?

140
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,220
If all six pieces

141
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,340
are used simultaneously,

142
00:09:35,590 --> 00:09:37,940
the boost to one's strength
is unimaginable.

143
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,460
Qian Renxue seems

144
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:43,119
to have acquired

145
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,940
a soul bone capable of dual disguises.

146
00:09:46,268 --> 00:09:48,440
I didn't even know such a skill existed.

147
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:50,829
I remember Qian Xunji
only had one daughter.

148
00:09:50,830 --> 00:09:53,460
She was announced dead
at the age of nine.

149
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:54,770
That

150
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,850
was twenty years ago.

151
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,730
If she's still alive,

152
00:10:00,190 --> 00:10:01,371
given her age,

153
00:10:01,372 --> 00:10:03,759
her soul power
should have reached level 70 or above,

154
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,220
which is incredibly talented.

155
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:08,340
When she possesses all six soul bones,

156
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:11,370
she will have the Angel's Armor

157
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:14,069
and gain the soul bone armor ability

158
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:15,460
like San's.

159
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,850
The increase in power

160
00:10:18,190 --> 00:10:19,890
is something we can't imagine.

161
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:22,820
With Qian Renxue's talent

162
00:10:23,470 --> 00:10:25,090
and the Angel's Armor,

163
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,730
her future strength

164
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,580
may rival even Bi Bi Dong's

165
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,250
or even

166
00:10:30,892 --> 00:10:32,568
stronger than Bi Bi Dong's.

167
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,752
But obtaining

168
00:10:34,430 --> 00:10:36,090
the Angel's Armor

169
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:37,940
isn't easy.

170
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:43,130
It's said

171
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,770
there's a requirement

172
00:10:46,028 --> 00:10:47,992
for absorbing the last soul bone.

173
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:50,010
One must reach level 100 soul power.

174
00:11:07,190 --> 00:11:08,667
In the history of soul masters,

175
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,789
increasing soul power by even one level

176
00:11:10,790 --> 00:11:12,189
after reaching level 90

177
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:13,403
is extremely difficult.

178
00:11:13,404 --> 00:11:14,399
I really don't know

179
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,159
what it's like to go

180
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,700
from level 99 to 100.

181
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,300
I know.

182
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,300
My father's

183
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,970
last opponent

184
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,300
was

185
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,060
a level 99 Grand Soul Master.

186
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:30,300
After defeating my father,

187
00:11:30,470 --> 00:11:31,460
he admitted

188
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,730
that he had spent 30 years trying

189
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:36,460
to reach level 100

190
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,090
but found no way.

191
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,660
He said

192
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:43,490
it isn't just a gap between level 99

193
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:44,820
and 100

194
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,490
but

195
00:11:47,292 --> 00:11:49,048
an insurmountable chasm.

196
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,820
Level 99?

197
00:11:51,644 --> 00:11:53,176
Who is this Grand Soul Master?

198
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,370
Head Flamen

199
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:58,580
of the Martial Soul Hall's Elder Hall,

200
00:11:58,988 --> 00:12:00,280
also the core leader

201
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,970
of the Martial Soul Hall,

202
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,220
Qian Renxue's grandfather,

203
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:09,010
Qian Daoliu.

204
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:18,660
Grandfather.

205
00:12:25,830 --> 00:12:27,090
You've met her?

206
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,300
Twenty years ago,

207
00:12:31,308 --> 00:12:32,940
she sent me to infiltrate Tiandou

208
00:12:33,070 --> 00:12:35,180
as a pawn in her game.

209
00:12:35,916 --> 00:12:38,069
Consider these twenty years
of undercover work

210
00:12:38,070 --> 00:12:40,060
a repayment for her raising me.

211
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,949
I didn't agree with her sending you

212
00:12:41,950 --> 00:12:43,060
to Tiandou

213
00:12:43,532 --> 00:12:45,279
because I was worried,
as you were so young.

214
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:47,010
But I have to admit one thing.

215
00:12:47,470 --> 00:12:49,370
Even though she was a bit rash,

216
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,220
she wasn't wrong.

217
00:12:52,070 --> 00:12:53,669
The position she's holding

218
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:54,730
isn't easy.

219
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:57,180
She had to be decisive and firm.

220
00:12:58,590 --> 00:12:59,970
And I want

221
00:13:00,070 --> 00:13:01,850
to be that way too.

222
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:04,970
Grandfather,

223
00:13:05,036 --> 00:13:06,619
I wish to follow in your footsteps

224
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,344
and take charge of the Elder Hall.

225
00:13:12,684 --> 00:13:14,069
Are you certain of this?

226
00:13:14,070 --> 00:13:16,039
The Elder Hall

227
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:18,669
isn't as powerful as it used to be.

228
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:19,730
At present,

229
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,540
Bi Bi Dong has more influence than me

230
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,180
in the Martial Soul Hall.

231
00:13:25,132 --> 00:13:26,920
It's a world of the strong,

232
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,940
and whoever is stronger

233
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,300
will have more say.

234
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,069
The Elder Hall

235
00:13:33,070 --> 00:13:34,460
should be supreme.

236
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,420
One day,

237
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:38,340
I'll make her realize that.

238
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,069
She's your mother, after all.

239
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:40,970
No, she's not!

240
00:13:41,950 --> 00:13:42,879
She never was,

241
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:43,999
not now,

242
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,300
not ever!

243
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,420
I will never forgive her.

244
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,060
Taking control of the Elder Hall

245
00:13:58,310 --> 00:13:59,460
is no simple task.

246
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,220
I do not have the final say on

247
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:03,220
whether you're qualified.

248
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:04,280
I understand.

249
00:14:04,764 --> 00:14:05,700
Grandfather,

250
00:14:06,364 --> 00:14:07,700
I must quickly absorb

251
00:14:07,710 --> 00:14:09,940
the second Angel's Armor soul bone.

252
00:14:10,124 --> 00:14:12,056
Please make the arrangement for me.

253
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:13,490
I believe

254
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:15,850
I will earn its approval.

255
00:14:21,196 --> 00:14:23,208
Our nation has faced great peril.

256
00:14:23,310 --> 00:14:24,610
But thanks to all of you,

257
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:26,180
who fought to the death,

258
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:29,010
our country is now safe.

259
00:14:29,710 --> 00:14:33,060
You are all heroes of Tiandou.

260
00:14:34,012 --> 00:14:35,239
Imperial Preceptor Yu

261
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,359
and Chief Ning,

262
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,608
please come forward.

263
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:41,730
In quelling the palace rebellion,

264
00:14:42,070 --> 00:14:45,039
Shrek Academy and the Qibao Amber Sect

265
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:46,584
have made great contributions.

266
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:48,060
By the imperial edict,

267
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,429
(Imperial Edict)

268
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:53,370
Ning Fengzhi will henceforth
be exempt from court bows

269
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,420
and shall assist
Imperial Preceptor Yu Xiaogang

270
00:14:56,430 --> 00:14:58,970
in training the royal soul masters

271
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:02,460
and commanding
all of Tiandou's soul masters.

272
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,610
Effective immediately,

273
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:49,010
the Fourth Prince Xue Beng

274
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:52,300
is crowned Crown Prince of Tiandou.

275
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:26,220
Qian Renxue has fled Tiandou,

276
00:16:27,190 --> 00:16:29,850
and the Martial Soul Hall's
ambitions know no bounds.

277
00:16:30,710 --> 00:16:32,060
A greater crisis

278
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,940
lies ahead.

279
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:36,420
For the peace of the continent,

280
00:16:36,710 --> 00:16:38,060
the safety of the people,

281
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,660
and the responsibilities we bear,

282
00:16:41,470 --> 00:16:42,300
Tiandou

283
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:44,250
must grow stronger.

284
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:45,940
Tiandou

285
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:49,060
must win!

286
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,789
Victory for Tiandou!

287
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:52,709
Victory for Tiandou!

