00:29:49,212 --> 00:29:49,639
Stop!

576
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,380
Ouch!

577
00:29:50,668 --> 00:29:51,509
Stop right there!

578
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:52,330
Run, huh?

579
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:53,970
Stay still!

580
00:29:55,612 --> 00:29:57,304
I dare you to run again!

581
00:29:57,452 --> 00:29:58,875
Since you're so eager to die,

582
00:29:58,876 --> 00:30:00,331
let me take care of that for you.

583
00:30:00,332 --> 00:30:01,675
Better that, than dying out there

584
00:30:01,676 --> 00:30:03,035
with no one to collect your bodies.

585
00:30:03,036 --> 00:30:03,771
It's infuriating.

586
00:30:03,772 --> 00:30:04,700
Mr. Yu,

587
00:30:04,990 --> 00:30:06,010
we have to go.

588
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:06,860
You...

589
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,180
You're no longer children.

590
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:14,730
You've faced countless dangers.

591
00:30:15,596 --> 00:30:17,119
Normally, I wouldn't interfere

592
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,530
with your future choices.

593
00:30:19,164 --> 00:30:20,770
But Haishen Island is different.

594
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:22,900
Even the Netherworld City pales

595
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:25,147
in comparison to it.

596
00:30:25,148 --> 00:30:26,770
Isn't that exactly what we need?

597
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,140
San,

598
00:30:28,220 --> 00:30:29,490
you're being reckless.

599
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:32,010
That place is a one-way trip.

600
00:30:32,710 --> 00:30:33,700
Do you know

601
00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:35,189
that Martial Soul Hall once sent...

602
00:30:35,190 --> 00:30:37,490
They once sent two thousand soul masters

603
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:39,643
to conquer the soul masters there.

604
00:30:39,644 --> 00:30:41,403
In the end, they returned defeated,

605
00:30:41,404 --> 00:30:43,469
losing two Grand Soul Masters
in the process.

606
00:30:43,470 --> 00:30:44,107
Since then,

607
00:30:44,108 --> 00:30:45,467
the Martial Soul Hall hasn't dared

608
00:30:45,468 --> 00:30:46,824
to target it again.

609
00:30:47,420 --> 00:30:49,304
Do you still want to train there

610
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:51,700
after knowing this?

611
00:30:51,750 --> 00:30:52,460
Mr. Yu,

612
00:30:52,668 --> 00:30:53,860
we're not going there

613
00:30:53,990 --> 00:30:56,220
to conquer the soul masters.

614
00:30:56,430 --> 00:30:58,460
We just want to improve ourselves.

615
00:30:58,524 --> 00:31:01,240
I don't think we'll end up like
the Martial Soul Hall, right?

616
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:04,250
You've certainly done your homework.

617
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,380
But you're still naive.

618
00:31:06,844 --> 00:31:08,189
Ocean soul masters

619
00:31:08,190 --> 00:31:10,730
are completely different from us.

620
00:31:10,990 --> 00:31:11,770
Sir,

621
00:31:12,076 --> 00:31:13,368
I know this one!

622
00:31:13,596 --> 00:31:15,189
Haishen Island soul masters draw

623
00:31:15,190 --> 00:31:16,491
their power from the sea.

624
00:31:16,492 --> 00:31:18,180
They're not friendly to outsiders.

625
00:31:18,316 --> 00:31:20,971
Their martial souls are mostly linked
to marine creatures,

626
00:31:20,972 --> 00:31:23,192
and their soul skills are different
from ours.

627
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:26,459
They harness the sea's power,

628
00:31:26,460 --> 00:31:28,920
giving them a natural advantage
over you.

629
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:30,919
Going there

630
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:32,669
is like walking into a lion's den.

631
00:31:32,670 --> 00:31:33,290
Plus,

632
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:34,970
Haishen Island

633
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:37,050
has a terrifying legend.

634
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:40,107
You even know this?

635
00:31:40,108 --> 00:31:40,747
All right.

636
00:31:40,748 --> 00:31:41,976
Tell me what you know.

637
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,380
I don't know.

638
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,509
Mr. Yu,

639
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,940
what did you mean

640
00:31:49,990 --> 00:31:51,660
by "legend"?

641
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:53,620
Why raise your hand if you don't know?

642
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,330
Xiaogang, ignore him.

643
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,635
Explain to them.

644
00:31:56,636 --> 00:31:57,669
So these kids understand

645
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:59,140
the danger of that place.

646
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:02,700
It's said Haishen Island is home
to a Grand Ocean God Master,

647
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:04,250
possibly

648
00:32:04,270 --> 00:32:06,220
a 99-Level Ultimate Soul Master.

649
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:09,159
She controls the ocean's power
for the God of the Ocean.

650
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,570
Soul masters going there

651
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:12,507
will face this power.

652
00:32:12,508 --> 00:32:13,599
As they face this power,

653
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:16,180
this power will rapidly increase.

654
00:32:16,510 --> 00:32:18,900
The soul masters' power will also grow,

655
00:32:19,670 --> 00:32:21,570
pushing them beyond their limits

656
00:32:21,670 --> 00:32:23,290
until it destroys them.

657
00:32:23,510 --> 00:32:24,250
So

658
00:32:24,470 --> 00:32:26,330
if this legend is true,

659
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,940
it's a death sentence if you go there.

660
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:30,010
Mr. Yu.

661
00:32:30,124 --> 00:32:31,531
Now that you've put it that way,

662
00:32:31,532 --> 00:32:32,879
we have even more reason

663
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,290
to head to Haishen Island.

664
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:35,490
Xiaogang,

665
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:37,290
look at these kids.

666
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:39,810
So these are the Little Devils
you've trained?

667
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,810
They're as stubborn as ever.

668
00:32:42,620 --> 00:32:43,900
Grinning, are you?

669
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,140
That's right.

670
00:32:45,676 --> 00:32:46,875
We, the Shrek Seven Devils,

671
00:32:46,876 --> 00:32:48,792
have never taken the ordinary path.

672
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:50,330
Mr. Yu,

673
00:32:50,332 --> 00:32:52,264
isn't this exactly what you taught us?

674
00:32:57,360 --> 00:33:00,220
I know you are concerned
about our safety.

675
00:33:00,284 --> 00:33:02,203
But once the Seven Clans
are restructured,

676
00:33:02,204 --> 00:33:04,330
the Martial Soul Hall
will surely expand.

677
00:33:04,892 --> 00:33:06,552
If we stay away from danger now,

678
00:33:06,710 --> 00:33:07,803
the Martial Soul Hall

679
00:33:07,804 --> 00:33:10,152
won't spare us
on the battlefield anyway.

680
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,283
If that legendary power

681
00:33:12,284 --> 00:33:14,424
can truly boost our soul power quickly,

682
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:16,620
why not take the risk?

683
00:33:18,710 --> 00:33:20,140
San is absolutely right.

684
00:33:20,172 --> 00:33:22,469
Taking a risk is better
than waiting for doom.

685
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:23,420
One day,

686
00:33:23,670 --> 00:33:26,570
Tiandou and Xingluo will
face Martial Soul Hall head-on.

687
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:28,639
If the younger soul masters like us,

688
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,730
hesitate,

689
00:33:29,950 --> 00:33:32,229
who will ensure peace
for the continent's future?

690
00:33:32,230 --> 00:33:33,051
Mubai and I

691
00:33:33,052 --> 00:33:35,269
have already informed the emperor
about Haishen Island.

692
00:33:35,270 --> 00:33:37,660
I believe he will support us.

693
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:43,010
You Little Devils...

694
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,180
It's my fault

695
00:33:45,270 --> 00:33:47,770
for raising you to be so fearless.

696
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:50,700
Now, I'm the one worried.

697
00:33:51,516 --> 00:33:52,330
All right.

698
00:33:52,732 --> 00:33:53,639
You can go.

699
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:54,180
Go.

700
00:33:55,430 --> 00:33:56,620
But know this,

701
00:33:57,360 --> 00:33:59,490
my knowledge about Haishen Island

702
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:02,100
and the ocean soul masters is limited.

703
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:04,180
Once you're there,

704
00:34:04,840 --> 00:34:06,970
you'll have to rely on yourselves.

705
00:34:07,756 --> 00:34:09,080
Don't worry, Mr. Yu.

706
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,810
Let's start getting ready.

707
00:34:12,940 --> 00:34:13,800
All right.

708
00:34:13,950 --> 00:34:14,989
But I have some matters

709
00:34:14,990 --> 00:34:17,190
that I need to return
to the Haotian Sect first.

710
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:19,180
Once I'm back,

711
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,580
we'll head to Haishen Island together.

712
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:51,290
(I've been afraid to disturb you,)

713
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,770
(or even think about you.)

714
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:56,370
(I hope you sleep well
in the Spiritual Sea.)

715
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:58,850
(But you've been asleep for so long.)

716
00:34:59,292 --> 00:35:01,272
(Why aren't you waking up yet?)

717
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,330
Cousin San,

718
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,290
Wu is still not awake?

719
00:35:31,868 --> 00:35:33,051
Cousin San,

720
00:35:33,052 --> 00:35:35,176
I heard you're going to Haishen Island.

721
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,239
Can that place

722
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:38,020
really boost soul power quickly?

723
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,620
That's what the legends say.

724
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:43,620
Then can I join you?

725
00:35:43,884 --> 00:35:45,679
I promise not to slow anyone down.

726
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:46,930
I can scout ahead

727
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,850
and clear any dangers.

728
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:50,069
You can let me handle anything

729
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:50,949
I can.

730
00:35:50,950 --> 00:35:51,700
Xiang,

731
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,730
you're the best scout we have.

732
00:35:54,030 --> 00:35:54,989
I'd be more than happy

733
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:56,410
to have you come along.

734
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:58,890
But

735
00:35:58,950 --> 00:36:01,450
this place could be very dangerous.

736
00:36:01,950 --> 00:36:03,275
As a soul master,

737
00:36:03,276 --> 00:36:06,279
you know that rapid power gains
come with equally great challenges,

738
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,410
and possibly the risk
of losing one's life.

739
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:09,832
I'm not afraid.

740
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,700
Grandfather is getting old

741
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,540
and still worries about me.

742
00:36:13,772 --> 00:36:15,707
I want to show him with my strength

743
00:36:15,708 --> 00:36:17,469
that no matter what happens,

744
00:36:17,470 --> 00:36:18,839
I can take care of him

745
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,890
and myself.

746
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:21,540
I don't need anyone's protection.

747
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:23,370
I can shoulder my responsibilities.

748
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:24,540
So

749
00:36:24,684 --> 00:36:26,888
no matter how dangerous
the path ahead is,

750
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:28,060
I'm not scared.

751
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:29,730
All right.

752
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:32,100
Then come with us.

753
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,003
Having you around

754
00:36:33,004 --> 00:36:35,128
will put my mind even more at ease.

755
00:36:35,372 --> 00:36:36,799
Thank you, Cousin San.

756
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,139
I'll make sure to scout safely

757
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:39,699
and clear any dangers for everyone.

758
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:41,509
I'm going to tell Grandfather
this good news.

759
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:42,290
Go.

760
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:56,140
Wu?

761
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,220
Wu,

762
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:01,930
you're finally awake.

763
00:37:27,510 --> 00:37:28,540
Wu.

764
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:29,890
Wu.

765
00:37:31,240 --> 00:37:32,500
Who are you?

766
00:37:34,252 --> 00:37:34,939
Don't you...

767
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:36,568
Don't you recognize me anymore?

768
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:39,211
I've never met you.

769
00:37:39,212 --> 00:37:40,968
Why should I recognize you?

770
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:45,540
Where is this place?

771
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:48,980
You said you were just going to sleep.

772
00:37:49,950 --> 00:37:51,220
How could you forget?

773
00:37:57,116 --> 00:37:58,440
Wait, don't do that.

774
00:37:58,470 --> 00:38:00,290
I was just kidding.

775
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,850
Kidding?

776
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,469
I was so worried about you.

777
00:38:05,470 --> 00:38:07,020
And you joke about this?

778
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:20,860
♪Longing is an unknown riddle♪

779
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:23,100
San,

780
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:27,700
don't be mad.

781
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:30,290
I didn't know you'd take it seriously.

782
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:33,290
I didn't consider your feelings.

783
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:36,020
Please don't be mad at me.

784
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:44,290
You dared to tease me?

785
00:38:48,204 --> 00:38:49,620
If you can joke with me,

786
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:51,250
why can't I do the same?

787
00:38:55,436 --> 00:38:56,587
When did you wake up?

788
00:38:56,588 --> 00:38:57,832
How are you feeling?

789
00:38:58,200 --> 00:39:00,770
I had a deep, restful sleep,

790
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,410
and I recovered quickly.

791
00:39:03,164 --> 00:39:05,848
I already woke up
when Xiang knocked on the door.

792
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:06,949
Say,

793
00:39:06,950 --> 00:39:09,589
if Fatty finds out Xiang is also going
to Haishen Island,

794
00:39:09,590 --> 00:39:10,850
he'll be over the moon.

795
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:12,330
He'll probably thank you.

796
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:14,580
Maybe even buy me some delicious food.

797
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:15,919
It looks like

798
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:18,200
you already know we're heading
to Haishen Island.

799
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:22,651
I'm really curious

800
00:39:22,652 --> 00:39:24,728
about what kind of place it will be.

801
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:26,020
Yeah,

802
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,450
me too.

803
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:32,799
(Tang Clan)

804
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:33,770
Elder Lou.

805
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:35,149
Chief,

806
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:35,629
good timing!

807
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:36,620
Come!

808
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:39,163
I've finished my work today.

809
00:39:39,164 --> 00:39:39,980
Look at this.

810
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:43,180
Young Master,

811
00:39:43,510 --> 00:39:46,379
we've completed
this batch of hidden weapons

812
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:48,251
for the Qibao Amber Sect
right on schedule.

813
00:39:48,252 --> 00:39:51,500
Thanks to Lou's help.

814
00:39:51,550 --> 00:39:52,589
We've been truly

815
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:54,020
unstoppable.

816
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:58,980
Good,

817
00:39:59,430 --> 00:40:00,155
very good.

818
00:40:00,156 --> 00:40:02,632
As expected from the God of Ironsmiths
of our time.

819
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:06,539
These hidden weapons are key
for the Tang Clan

820
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:08,370
to stand up against Martial Soul Hall.

821
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:09,890
Chief,

822
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,429
I've completed the tasks

823
00:40:11,430 --> 00:40:12,919
you gave me.

824
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,660
Don't forget what you promised.

825
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:17,799
Who is the person

826
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,227
who will help me make

827
00:40:19,228 --> 00:40:20,635
the Storm Pear Blossom Needles?

828
00:40:20,636 --> 00:40:22,290
When will we meet him?

829
00:40:22,430 --> 00:40:24,730
I'm here to discuss that.

830
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:26,410
Elder Lou,

831
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:28,552
follow me back to the Haotian Sect.

832
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:38,020
Watch your step.

833
00:41:13,740 --> 00:41:15,359
So this is where the Haotian Sect

834
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,850
is hidden.

835
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:38,580
Tang San?

836
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:39,429
You're back.

837
00:41:39,430 --> 00:41:40,315
Tang Long,

838
00:41:40,316 --> 00:41:41,704
it's been a while.

839
00:41:45,932 --> 00:41:47,180
Who are these people?

840
00:41:47,484 --> 00:41:49,515
As a disciple of the Haotian Sect,
you should know

841
00:41:49,516 --> 00:41:51,659
after the Haotian Sect withdrew
from the world,

842
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:53,339
no one other than
the Haotian Sect members

843
00:41:53,340 --> 00:41:54,440
was allowed inside.

844
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:55,930
I know the rules.

845
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:57,199
So I need your help

846
00:41:57,200 --> 00:41:59,029
to watch over my friends outside

847
00:41:59,030 --> 00:42:00,651
while I inform the Chief

848
00:42:00,652 --> 00:42:01,799
and get permission

849
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,850
to bring them in.

850
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:04,100
No matter.

851
00:42:04,590 --> 00:42:06,220
Tang San understands the rules.

852
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:08,580
Bring your friends inside.

853
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:09,930
Tang Long,

854
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,810
inform the elders.

855
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:13,980
Tell them Tang San has returned.

856
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:14,890
Yes.

857
00:42:16,156 --> 00:42:17,400
Please come inside.

858
00:42:17,612 --> 00:42:18,808
This way, please.

859
00:42:21,590 --> 00:42:22,500
Chief,

